OL,3,CHome Secretary: Police failing to take
OL,4,Cviolence against women 'seriously'
OL,6,FThe Home Secretary has told ITV News
OL,7,Fviolence against women and girls has
OL,8,Fnot been taken "seriously" by police
OL,9,F"for far too long".
OL,11,FYvette Cooper said an "overhaul" of
OL,12,Fthe way police respond to domestic
OL,13,Fabuse, stalking and assaults on
OL,14,Ffemales was needed.
OL,16,FMs Cooper said: "I think violence
OL,17,Fagainst women and girls, domestic
OL,18,Fabuse, sexual assault and stalking
OL,19,Fhaven't been taken seriously by
OL,20,Fpolicing for too long. We have to
OL,21,Fchange that.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/7
