OL,3,CHome Secretary: Police failing to take
OL,4,Cviolence against women 'seriously'
OL,6,F"I think this is really serious. We've
OL,7,Fgot to have much stronger action
OL,8,Fagainst domestic abuse, stalking and
OL,9,Fthis serious violence against women
OL,10,Fand girls. That means we need to have
OL,11,Fan overhaul in the way in which
OL,12,Fpolicing responds."
OL,14,FThe Home Secretary's comments were in
OL,15,Fresponse to an ITV News Calendar
OL,16,Finvestigation which revealed how at
OL,17,Fleast 18 women were killed in the last
OL,18,Ffive years by men who were already
OL,19,Fknown to police forces in Yorkshire
OL,20,Fand Lincolnshire.
