OL,3,CHome Secretary: Police failing to take
OL,4,Cviolence against women 'seriously'
OL,6,FThey also came on the day three
OL,7,FMetropolitan Police officers were
OL,8,Ffound guilty of gross misconduct after
OL,9,Fthey accessed files relating to the
OL,10,FSarah Everard case with "no proper
OL,11,Fpolicing purpose".
OL,13,FMs Everard was kidnapped raped and
OL,14,Fmurdered by serving Met Police
OL,15,Fofficer, Wayne Couzens in March 2021.
OL,17,FThe National Police Chiefs' Council
OL,18,F(NPCC) estimates that two million
OL,19,Fwomen are victims of male violence
OL,20,Fevery year and has described the
OL,21,Fproblem as a "national emergency".
