OL,3,CHome Secretary: Police failing to take
OL,4,Cviolence against women 'seriously'
OL,6,FLabour has pledged to halve violence
OL,7,Fagainst women and girls in a decade.
OL,9,FMs Cooper said: "We need to see
OL,10,Fdomestic abuse experts in 999 control
OL,11,Fcentres so they hear what's going on.
OL,13,F"We need a training overhaul for
OL,14,Fpolicing and also new protection
OL,15,Forders in place so stronger action is
OL,16,Ftaken.
OL,18,F"We are bringing in new requirements
OL,19,Fon training on these sorts of crimes
OL,20,Ffor police officers across the country.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/7
