OL,3,CHome Secretary: Police failing to take
OL,4,Cviolence against women 'seriously'
OL,6,F"But also a requirement to have
OL,7,Fdomestic abuse experts in 999 control
OL,8,Frooms - to have action locally and
OL,9,Fexperts who know how serious these
OL,10,Fcrimes are with new powers, protection
OL,11,Forders. We have to have action across
OL,12,Fthe board."
OL,14,FThe NPCC says it is "absolutely
OL,15,Fdetermined" to tackle the problem.
