OL,6,FDeputy Ch Con Maggie Blyth, the NPCC's
OL,7,Flead for violence against women and
OL,8,Fgirls, said: "Our focus will always be
OL,9,Fto bring the men behind these
OL,10,Fpervasive crimes to justice. By
OL,11,Fenhancing the way we use data and
OL,12,Fintelligence, we will improve our
OL,13,Fability to identify, intercept and
OL,14,Farrest those causing the most harm in
OL,15,Fcommunities.
